UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = '“The key to understanding the mind is to understand the way it works,” the scientist said, “and to do that, we need to look at how the mind processes information.”  This sentence establishes that the scientist is arguing for a more active and engaged approach to understanding the mind, rather than a passive approach that simply focuses on the mind’s contents. What is the most likely reason why the writer uses the phrase “to do that?”',
